{"tid":2013272,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港黃圈可唔可採用類似加盟形式","createTime":"2020-05-12T07:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T06:38:49.000Z","uid":306592,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c3fdf19f9426ae18d76dd735667db2af8f3039a3","tid":2013272,"uid":306592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"用加盟模式結合所有黃店是否可行？<br />\n<br />\n建立一間公司做icon<br />\n<br />\n其他黃店加盟呢間公司但同時繼續保持自己獨立性<br />\n<br />\n用黎擴大呢間公司既資產價值方便進行海外既擴展<br />\n<br />\n呢間公司唔會壟斷本地市場而係專心發展環球業務<br />\n<br />\n方便集資而且所有黃店可以進行監察作用"},{"pid":"2001b71d247c842e880d661c8b6fc07196e231e7","tid":2013272,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:46:01.000Z","msg":"政府會打壓"},{"pid":"5a4a4b0959b372be1044de1c33a7cd17cfbfd7a7","tid":2013272,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"間公司會好腐敗"},{"pid":"b59bbbb6b22d9bd335a50ec3daddb2faf307d258","tid":2013272,"uid":306592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2001b71d247c842e880d661c8b6fc07196e231e7","tid":2013272,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:46:01.000Z","msg":"政府會打壓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"如果新公司係海外成立<br />\n<br />\n做一個跨國加盟<br />\n<br />\n香港既黃店本身就存在"},{"pid":"700e97906cd51b29fa46a8ad688eae4a56a566da","tid":2013272,"uid":55300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;係咪即係大台呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1610e54bb8d7373c30c157260e40297e390621ef","tid":2013272,"uid":306592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a4a4b0959b372be1044de1c33a7cd17cfbfd7a7","tid":2013272,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"間公司會好腐敗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"但係佢無干預其他公司權力<br />\n<br />\n公司搵知名人士做icon<br />\n<br />\n管理請專家"},{"pid":"d6c08c25ea6b09425c7