,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"之前咪有人搞過<br />\n收認證費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f001030f424acdcfe8f81cf3aa157b12fb05c38","tid":2013272,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"各間公司保持獨立性，但係又要統一icon。<br />\n無權但係又擁有哂所有資產，咁到底邊個有權運用依啲資產？<br />\n無權又發展咩業務？<br />\n無權又點樣進行監察？"},{"pid":"b8a3eb07af19ce2a447db4a82948ae67988c92e6","tid":2013272,"uid":306592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:00:49.000Z","msg":"我唔清楚加盟費係稅前定稅後比<br />\n如果稅前比就 計返個比率收<br />\n令黃店交俾政府嘅稅轉移一部份去呢間店"},{"pid":"244134b3cf829810d8321b84d0867f7d2b8d0a46","tid":2013272,"uid":306592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5499cba647657a25f230f7f4e870adcddebad7f1","tid":2013272,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"之前咪有人搞過<br />\n收認證費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T08:03:22.000Z","msg":"其實我主要係諗香港人要成立東印度公司嘅初始模式"},{"pid":"c767b1ff6ea73c8cbc8f01d20d912ad3d48c2f7d","tid":2013272,"uid":4351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:38:49.000Z","msg":"你諗清楚你講緊乜先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間公司無權管理黃店 黃店又始終係獨立個體<br />\n<br />\n間公司又要宣傳 又要專家管理<br />\n<br />\n但黃店又唔使俾返錢佢 咁間公司啲錢係咪你俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}